cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence, hence cs.LG and cs.AI are the most likely categories. The use of images as input suggests that the paper may also belong to the computer vision category (cs.CV). The paper also deals with designing subtasks and decomposing the state space, which are topics related to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
